## Example equation

Here is an example equation:

$$

## Example table

```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(knitr)
library(faraway)
data(worldcup)

table_example <- worldcup %>% 
  slice(1:6) %>% 
  select(Team, Position, Time, Shots)

kable(table_example)
```
